text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This obsoletes IRM 4.61.4, International Examination Guidelines, Information Gathering.

This IRM is obsolete. See the Information Gathering Knowledge Management site for informational resources (e.g. Issuing a Formal Document Request when a US Taxpayer is Unresponsive to an IDR Practice Unit) or contact the Information Gathering Practice Network team. Relevant topics can also be found in IRM 4.46.4, LB&I Examination Process, Executing the Examination and IRM 4.61.3, International Examination Guidelines, Development of IRC 482 Cases.
EFFECT ON OTHER DOCUMENTS IRM 4.61.4 dated May 01, 2006 is obsolete.
Acting Assistant Deputy Commissioner Compliance Integration Large Business and International Division
